TOP NAVBAR:
  - "GRAPHENE" wordmark left
  - System status indicator (green dot + "LIVE")
  - Last scan time
  - "Run Full Scan" button (triggers POST /api/scan → refreshes all data)

TECH STACK FOR FRONTEND:
  - React 18 via CDN (unpkg)
  - Cytoscape.js via CDN for graph
  - Fetch API for all data loading (no Axios needed)
  - CSS custom properties for theming — no Tailwind, no component library
  - All in a SINGLE index.html file for portability

BEHAVIOUR:
  - On load: fetch /api/alerts/stats → populate top bar
             fetch /api/alerts?tier=CRITICAL&limit=20 → populate alert queue
             auto-select first alert → load its graph
  - When alert selected: fetch /api/graph/{account_id}?depth=2
                         render in Cytoscape → animate nodes fading in
                         load SHAP explanation → render bars
  - "Generate FIU Report" → POST /api/reports/generate → open PDF in new tab
  - Polling: every 30 seconds re-fetch alerts (simulates live monitoring)
